Ge_tower version 6

By os-Genome

Terrorists have taken over a very weird looking tower which has a spinny light thing at the top.

Objective is to kill all enemies. There are three ways for the CTs to reach the top of the tower. A ladder on the outside of the tower, an elevator, and a ladder behind the elevator. Beware of explosive barrels.

CT:  Kill the terrorists.

T:  Kill the counter-terrorists.

HINT: You can shoot the barrels before they fall down, killing the people who released them.

And don't block the elevator. You'll die in exactly 0.6 seconds.
